'''查尔斯·埃默森'''（{{lang-en|Charles Emmerson}}，{{bd|1976年|}}）是一位[[英国|英国]][[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]双重国籍的[[历史学家|历史学家]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chathamhouse.org/experts|title=Experts|website=Chatham House|access-date=2020-12-29|archive-date=2019-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108122714/https://www.chathamhouse.org/experts|dead-url=no}}</ref>，出生于[[墨尔本|墨尔本]]，成长于[[伦敦|伦敦]]，在[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]学习现代史，后进入[[查塔姆研究所|查塔姆研究所]]工作，主要作品有《1913：一战前的世界》（''1913: The World Before the Great War''）等<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/b52a3198-27e4-11df-9598-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2Vu2L0Alq |title=FT review of ''Arctic'' |access-date=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307164309/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/b52a3198-27e4-11df-9598-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2Vu2L0Alq |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url= https://www.theguardian.com/books/2013/may/08/1913-world-before-great-review| title= 1913: The World Before the Great War by Charles Emmerson - review| last= Hughes| first= Kathryn| authorlink= Kathryn Hughes| date= 8 May 2013| accessdate= 30 January 2020| archive-date= 2020-05-24| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200524001146/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2013/may/08/1913-world-before-great-review| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

